ction figures, and are in scale with one another.</p>\n',13,4538,2,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-05-24 20:28:23','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(84,NULL,22,'Gus Fink\'s Boogily Heads','gus-finks-boogily-heads','<p>An extensive series of mini-sculptures created by Gus Fink &amp; produced by Rocket USA. Each figure includes a mini-comic backed with a poster, and all have bobble-head action!</p>\n',24,2049,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-06-05 11:17:09','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(85,NULL,102,'June 6 2008 Garage Sale Finds','june-6-2008-garage-sale-finds','<p>These are some things I bought at garage sales on June 6 2008</p>\n',13,1912,3,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-06-14 03:46:06','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(86,NULL,57,'Garbage Pail Kids','garbage-pail-kids','<p>Mixed Topps GPK Series -- cards from the mid 80\'s.</p>\n',102,10880,7,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-06-16 03:20:43','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(87,NULL,11,'Continental Collection','continental-collection','<p>I collect all things \"Continental\". </p>\n',7,983,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-06-24 17:17:53','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(88,NULL,7,'Metal art','metal-art','<p>Our collection is too large to post together so I\'ve split it into Metal art, Ceramics, Glass and Graphic art.</p>\n',60,1968,5,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-06-25 16:15:32','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(89,NULL,7,'Wood collection','wood-collection','<p>Everything we collect has a high degree of difficulty. Our wood pieces are no exception.</p>\n',26,2081,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-06-25 21:56:38','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(90,NULL,7,'My Altered Art','my-altered-art','<p>My attempts to brave the \"destruction\" of old paper &amp; make art of it. You can read about it here: http://xrl.us/oo2br</p>\n',3,1185,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-06-30 05:43:05','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(91,NULL,102,'Dinosaur Pez','dinosaur-pez','<p>In honor of  Dinosaur week -