5,NULL,102,'September 5th Weekend Haul','september-5th-weekend-haul','<p>It was a good weekend for me and my dinosaur collection.  On Friday I received a box of dinosaur toys in the mail from my father in law (he knows I collect them and he buys them for me when he comes across them).  On Saturday I went to an estate sale that had some dinosaur toys.  And also on Saturday my wife was at a garage sale and found a huge box full of dinosaur toys!  On Sunday I returned to the estate sale to pick up some more dinosaur toys that I passed on the day before - they were half price on Sunday!  Total amount I spent for everything you see here: $13.50</p>\n',50,2254,4,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-09-07 10:29:28','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(116,NULL,2,'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles','teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles','<p>A variety of TMNT incarnations, as action figures.</p>\n',3,1764,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-10-03 21:07:24','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(117,NULL,34,'Hellboy','hellboy','<p>A wide array of Hellboy collectibles, including original film props and many action figures.</p>\n\n<p>Also included, but not pictured, is the complete Mezco comic series (all 8, including the ultra-rare Kriegaffe #10), plus Comic Con Abe Sapien &amp; Floating Head Hellboy.</p>\n\n<p>1:1 Sideshow Samitan replica gun, Abe Sapien 1:2 bust, Hot Toys Hellboy &amp; Abe, Ultimate 12\" Sideshow Hellboy, faux bronze Mezco HB bust, Mezco\'s extreme Hellboy, Selma Blair\'s cross necklace from the first film, and Jeffrey Tambor\'s pants - as well as a lot of other stuff!</p>\n',39,2470,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-10-03 21:10:41','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(118,NULL,102,'Prehistoric Puzzles','prehistoric-puzzles','<p>These are some of the prehistoric-themed puzzles I have</p>\n',11,1085,1,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-10-12 11:33:42','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(119,NULL,55,'Toys and Collectibles','toys-and-collectibles','<p>In my quest to collect dinosaur toys sometimes I come across other cool toys that I do not have room to store, so I must sell them!  And sometimes I even sell dinosaur toys too!</p>\n',5,1267,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-11-07 10:53:09','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(120,NULL,489,'Travel &amp; Tourism','travel-amp-tourism','<p>Postcards, maps, travel brochures, and other assorted ephemera.</p>\n',26,2119,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-11-09 05:09:59','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(121,NULL,13,'Chalkware &amp; Plaster','chalkware-amp-plaster','<p>Vintage chalkware, retro plaster; figurines, wall plaques.  See my article here at Collectors\' Quest on chalkware: http://xrl.us/owrss</p>\n',13,2779,2,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2009-03-16 18:29:01','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(122,NULL,55,'Onell Design Figures','onell-design-figures','<p>A collection of small art-action-figures from Onell Design [onelldesign.com].</p>\n',12,1106,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-11-09 10:55:05','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(123,NULL,171,'Vintage Magazines','vintage-magazines','<p>Piles &amp; piles of \'em.</p>\n',55,3976,15,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2009-10-06 06:57:32','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(124,NULL,683,'Buck Rogers Disintegrator Pistol by Go Hero','buck-rogers-disintegrator-pistol-by-go-hero','<p>A limited edition of 1000 reproduction Daisy Buck Rogers Atomic Disintegrator Pistols, made beautifully by Go Hero.</p>\n',19,2030,1,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-11-26 00:25:36','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(125,NULL,2,'Doctor Who Action Figures','doctor-who-action-figures','<p>A collection of Dr. Who figures from Character Options in the UK.</p>\n',15,1754,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2009-11-22 14:52:07','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(126,NULL,43,'The Real Ghostbusters : Complete Collection on DVD','the-real-ghostbusters-complete-collection-on-dvd','<p>A beautiful $180 set released by Time-Life, which includes 25 DVDs in 5 metal cases, in fancy, lenticular firehouse packaging.</p>\n',13,1382,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-11-28 19:41:41','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(127,NULL,55,'Jurassic Park III Dino Packs Dinosaurs','jurassic-park-iii-dino-packs-dinosaurs','<p>This collection provides information about the Jurassic Park III Dino Packs dinosaur toys, a short-lived series of miniature figures that I think are very underrated.</p>\n',12,2503,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-12-03 11:44:46','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(128,NULL,66,'Dogs (That Don\'t Fit In Anywhere Else)','dogs-that-dont-fit-in-anywhere-else','<p>Dogs I have ended up with, rescued -- or have followed me home somehow... Other dogs can also be found in other collections too. (See here for my chalkware for the large dogs! http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/813/chalkware-plaster.html And here for my dog figurines with fur too http://xrl.us/oz84o</p>\n',8,1268,1,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2009-11-16 18:42:11','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(129,NULL,3,'I Collect Soap?!','i-collect-soap','<p>I call them figural soaps -- because soap figurines sounds too fancy &amp; I don\'t know what else to call them... Maybe just old soaps?</p>\n',5,1969,6,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-12-07 05:32:49','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(130,NULL,313,'Elves, Pixies, Whatever','elves-pixies-whatever','<p>Elves, pixies, imps, whatever you call them.  Kitsch goodness. Vintage &amp; retro; cloth, plastic and ceramic.</p>\n',8,1894,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-12-07 05:49:29','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(131,NULL,51,'nordstrom snowglobes','nordstrom-snowglobes','<p>Little winter fairies</p>\n',7,1135,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-12-12 16:16:47','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(132,NULL,51,'Christmas','christmas','<p>Christmas Snowglobes</p>\n',9,1020,3,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2008-12-12 16:36:22','2012-02-10 13:02:56','CollectorCollection'),(133,NULL,51,'Around the World','around-the-world','<p>My friends love me! :)</p>\n',28,1037