NULL,'2009-10-31 15:59:31','2012-02-10 13:02:57','CollectorCollection'),(221,NULL,22,'Cougars,lynxs and caracals','cougarslynxs-and-caracals','<p>Watch for new items from time to time!</p>\n',5,1264,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2010-02-14 15:32:48','2012-02-10 13:02:57','CollectorCollection'),(222,NULL,22,'Tigers','tigers','<p>Watch for new items every once in a while!</p>\n',7,1017,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2009-10-31 16:31:50','2012-02-10 13:02:57','CollectorCollection'),(223,NULL,116,'Robert Balser and The Museum of UnCut Funk','robert-balser-and-the-museum-of-uncut-funk','<p>The Museum Of UnCut Funk presents our interview with Robert Balser, Supervising Director of The Jackson Five Cartoon. Bob talks to us about his illustrious career, and in particular his involvement with The Jackson Five Cartoon and how important it was to create a positive animated series for Black children during the 1970\'s.</p>\n',5,463,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2009-11-28 20:42:09','2012-02-10 13:02:57','CollectorCollection'),(224,NULL,329,'Dinosaur Movie Memorabilia','dinosaur-movie-memorabilia','<p>Mainly dinosaur memorabilia such as props posters standees promos figures cells art and autographs.</p>\n',5,1483,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2009-11-12 14:54:34','2012-02-10 13:03:50','CollectorCollection'),(225,NULL,6,'Antique &amp; Vintage Purses','antique-amp-vintage-purses','<p>Antique bags, vintage handbags, etc.</p>\n',2,1142,1,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2009-11-16 07:02:18','2012-02-10 13:02:57','CollectorCollection'),(226,NULL,22,'Pinnipeds','pinnipeds','<p>Walruses,seals and sea lions.Whatch from time to time for new items!</p>\n',5,756,0,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2009-11-28 14:04:05','2012-02-10 13:02:57','CollectorCollection'),(227,NULL,22,'Cetaceans','cetaceans','<p>Whales and dolphins.Watch from time to time for new items!</p>\n',20,2084,1,0,0,1,0,1,1,NULL,'2009-12-29 15:09:39','2012-02-10 13:02:57','CollectorCollection'),(228,NULL,22,'Bony fish','bony-fish','<p>Watch from time to time for new items!</p>\n',20,1891,1,0,0,1